    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: Mechanick JI, Kushner RF, Sugerman HJ, Gonzalez-Campoy JM, Collazo-Clavell ML, Guven S, Spitz AF, Apovian CM, Livingston EH, Brolin R, Sarwer DB, Anderson WA, Dixon J. American Association of Clinical Endocrinologists, the Obesity Society, and American Society for Metabolic and Bariatric Surgery Medical guidelines for clinical practice for the perioperative nutritional, metabolic, and nonsurgical support [trunc]. Endocr Pract. 2008 Jul-Aug;14(Suppl 1):1-83.</p></div></p>
